                    <p><emph><ref corresp="mailto:irene.vagionakis2@unibo.it">Irene Vagionakis</ref></emph></p>
                    <p>I graduated in Classics (BA, 2013) and Ancient History (MA, 2015) at the University of Bologna and I obtained a PhD at the University of Venice Ca’ Foscari (2020) with a dissertation in Greek epigraphy / Digital epigraphy. 
                        I have been working on digital epigraphy projects since 2014, collaborating with IGCyr, AIO, Axon, GIO, EDV, IRCyr, IRT.
                        Since 2020 I am a research fellow in Digital Humanities at the Department of History and Cultures of the University of Bologna.</p>
